('100061930', NULL, 'users/117283651/ruth-25', 'I must comment that this quality :"-Be aware that there are people who you cannot help" means that you shoudnt feel on the duty to be hepfull to everyone who has a problem...If the problem affects you in a wrong way, or if you cannot empathize or understand to your patient, you should admit, in mi opinion', '03 Jun ''13, 15:55', '100061914'),
