('100062095', NULL, 'users/100007518/andyatudacity', 'This measure of correlation doesn''t take into account what happens first. If you can state a relationship as "When x increases, y decreases," it''s a negative correlation. So here "as alcohol consumption increases, physical coordination decreases."', '03 Jun ''13, 18:01', '100062086'),
