('100063139', NULL, 'users/113836624/halfknot', 'I don''t think Wikipedia said they are completely unrelated. If you actually read what I pasted, Wikipedia only pointed out that they are not identical. Your "introverts or shy people" comment makes the listener believe you are implying they are interchangeable. \n\nOther than that, I found your comment regarding my critical thinking ironic, as you tell me not to believe a certain internet source, but believe the other (i.e. not believe the article cited in Wikipedia which references an article written by a doctor in psychology, but believe your unreferenced comment) But if you read what I wrote, you''d understand you''re both saying the same thing - shyness and introversion are correlated to some degree, but not enough to be interchangeable as you seem to infer in the video.\n\nAgain, sorry for my "tone", but apparently I can''t help it.', '04 Jun ''13, 14:13', '100063105'),
