('100065212', NULL, 'users/100053416/francis-geist', 'ok so if there isn''t a cause, what can one deduce or make out of the correlations.  I''m just not understanding the point of  finding out the negative and positive. I know the direction in the sex and chores example is positive but, what it''s the point in finding out what is positive even if one can''t find the cause?', '06 Jun ''13, 17:58', '100065204'),
