('100073331', 'Will the environment affect the genes of ourselves?', 'Intro to Psychology - Lesson 03 Problem Set - Problem 21', '\nThe environment can affect what genes are turned on or off, thus affecting our traits.\n The environment can affect what genes are turned on or off, thus affecting our traits. So the environment factors will not only affect our offsprings'' traits, but will also turn on or off our genes?', 'users/119717931/', '18 Jun ''13, 23:49', 166, 0, 1),
