('100073652', 'About ambivalent-anxious attachment in problem set', 'Intro to Psychology - Lesson 05 Problem Set - Problem 14', 'Hi! In the lectures says that in ambivalent-anxious attachment babies are upset most of the time and specially upset (in the picture the baby is crying) when their care-taker leaves. In the problem set though, says that in AA attachement babies don''t cry when their mother leaves. Which is the one ? Thanks!', 'users/119017908/marcos-62', '19 Jun ''13, 11:13', 674, 33, 10),
