('100099625', 'Will there be different levels of certification for those who complete this course?', 'null', 'After looking through the forums I noticed some of the people who took this course last year mentioned different levels of certification depending on their performance. I realise it''s likely that this course has changed somewhat since then, though was wondering whether there would still be different levels of certification (accomplishment, distinction, etc)? Either way, I am really enjoying the course and looking forward to the final lessons becoming available. I''ve learned so much through the lessons so far! ', 'users/126278157/amanda-69', '04 Aug ''13, 07:37', 270, 0, 3),
