('100105628', 'Introduction to Psychology Lesson 06 Consciousness: suggestions', 'Intro to Psychology - Lesson 06 Consciousness - Hallucinogens', 'Another comment: Hey doc, my perception changed since I''m taking the hallucinogen a day. Doc: "you must have hallucinations" can you please loosen up the drug part a bit? It''s a lot of information. And -in general- can you please avoid the audio cuts while talking (I know it has to be synchronized to the animations but I really prefer the fluent talk if possible) As an example: I didn''t like the cuts in Lesson 06 Consciousness: sleep stages\nsincerely Marcus     ', 'users/100104209/marcus', '20 Aug ''13, 11:42', 183, 0, 1),
