('100132781', 'And the answer is... dragons.', 'Intro to Psychology - Lesson 02 Problem Set - Problem 19', 'I gave "Dragons" as the answer. It said I was correct. I''m pretty sure that''s not correct. Is there really a point to this type of question if there is no way for the computer to tell if the answer is reasonably correct or not?', 'users/118943184/jack-140', '04 Dec ''13, 07:38', 295, 2, 4),
