('100077388', '100077370', 'users/118531404/sonja-7', 'this means that your mom has genes for blue eyes and genes for brown eyes, but her phenotype is brown eyes because brown is dominant here. Your dad has blue eyes, so he has inherited genes for blue eyes from both his parents. If you have blue eyes that means you have also inherited the genes for blue eyes from both your parents - from your dad, because he could only "give" you the genes for blue eyes. With your mom you had a 50 % chance of getting either the genes for blue or brown eyes, but you got the blue eyes.', '24 Jun ''13, 14:56', 3),
