('100078142', '100077370', 'users/117873581/beatriz-16', 'That means that at least one of your mother''s ''ancestors'' (your grandparents, or grandgrandparents, or even grandgrandparents, etc.) had blue eyes, and the blue allele was inherited from one generation to the next, maybe for a long time.\nThis allele could have been ''hidden'' for many generations if it always had to ''compete'' with a stronger one, as the brown allele, which was obviously the case of your mother.\nNow, you and your siblings have inherited the blue allele from your father (having blue eyes, that''s the only onw he could give you) and also from your mother (as Sonja explains, that was a 50% chance), so your eyes are blue as well :)', '25 Jun ''13, 16:45', 1),
