('100082357', '100081869', 'users/115226568/lauren-castellano', 'Hi Soodipto,\n     There are a number of things licensed professionals can do to help with night terrors. For example some sleep aids, medication to help relax a person, and even different types of therapy. The person we interviewed about night terrors was offered different types of medications to help him relax however, the doctors he spoke with also emphasized the importance of managing stress and psychological well-being. Everyone is different so it is difficult to say what exactly one should do if they have night terrors other than consult their doctor.', '02 Jul ''13, 18:18', 4),
