('100090593', '100089926', 'users/120191717/andre-luiz-1', 'That''s my point of view:\nSmiling is a natural response of happiness and, at the same time, it is also a very powerful weapon that can change not only our mood, but also the mood of others around us. It is so powerful that can enlighten the atmosphere around us. All of that with a single smile. Yes, smiles are contagious.\nBut .......\nAlthough smile is a natural response of happiness, it is not the happiness itself, The happiness is a state of mind, a state of mind peace (it is something that has to be cultivate). And somebody who is happy (has/cultivates this state of mind) can smile easily and can deal better with the difficulties of life. In that way, the difficulties of life cannot disturb, for a long time, a person who is happy.\nTo put it quite simple: It is said that the pain is inevitable, but the suffering is optional.\nAndr', '16 Jul ''13, 21:28', 1),
