('100091362', '100090801', 'users/125222864/max-167', 'But you can help it.  The idea of a reflex is that it''s done involuntarily when there is a stimulus.  Like when the doctor hits below your knee and you kick.  The whole idea is that there is no thought behind it.  When an room full of people are all clapping, sure, the idea is to clap along with them, but it''s not something you do without thinking.', '18 Jul ''13, 03:33', 2),
