('100091365', '100074995', 'users/125222864/max-167', 'No one ever said you had to go through all the steps, or in order.  It''s a common misconception.  When you look at the actual book and research it never states this.  That aside, bargaining has nothing to do with god.  In a sense it''s really just an extension of denial.  It''s the idea that a person is desperately trying to work around something that is essentially inevitable.  It has no connection to the existence of god at all.', '18 Jul ''13, 03:35', 0),
