('100091416', '100089926', 'users/117967188/pardeep-3', 'Well in my view we only smile when we are happy, in fact that is a logical physical expression of being happy inside. And sometimes i am just down and i then will have a hard time trying to put on a smile. \n                     One day i was in college and i had to talk to my college''s clerk about the scholarship i was entitled to but did not receive, i was upset, but instead i tried to put on a smile and talk to him cheerfully. It turned out that he returned this with a smile and answered my query happily. that day i realized that smiling cannot solve the problem, but it can certainly bring our BP down and can also make us see more happy faces around us :-D', '18 Jul ''13, 06:13', 0),
