('100100653', '100093579', 'users/117588655/julirn', 'Hello!\nWell, I would simply say, if misused masturbation can be a risky thing. \nLet''s focus first on a less emotional theme, for example food. Food is something absolutely normal, natural and necessary thing; and I guess hardly anyone would disagree with this statement. However, there are people who suffer from anorexia or bulimia or many other diseases; but it is not the food itself that is to blame here. \nSimilarly, "obsessive" masturbation might be the expression of a deeper problem; but again, I do not think that the masturbation ITSELF is to blame. The real problems are very often others. \nGru\nJulien Caussin', '06 Aug ''13, 14:43', 19),
