('100115796', '100100635', 'users/121166559/iulia-5', 'Hi Marcus,\nI''m not sure what wasn''t precise. I was merely stating that we cannot use Maslow''s hierarchy of needs without taking into account the urgency of those needs.\nPutting needs on a scale from 1 to 5 (1 - completely unsatisfied; 5 completely satisfied), one can see how a man with hunger 1 and loneliness 1 would rather eat, but how he might go to the movies instead if his hunger was 3.', '24 Sep ''13, 16:13', 0),
