('100149819', '100128872', 'users/113682554/dhaval', 'As per the video chomsky talked about language being a more structure that we learn effortlessly,whereas skinner was of the view that language like other things can be taught and learned and is functional in approach.I feel structural functional relationship can be discussed on any thing we want to discuss upon.A structure is some what built in tools available upon which one builts upon.Its a framework which is partly a pool from nature and partly evolutionary in nature which progresses as one evolves.so when chomsky said that we dont learn language during early childhood its natural and a part of world heritage ,he means all humans barring exception comes with a similar brain and body which are nature tools.So our sub-conscious mind picks up language just like any other human beings mind .If a small group of people speaks a common language there is already a stock of vocabulary or language available which is exposed to the new-born baby and during its early childhood.This structure is all that is needed if the stock has expanded by evolution or is rudimentary in early evolution, to pick things up.\nWhereas skinner talks of language is a function of its usage.Once a child is exposed it learns to use the language as per its need and conditioning .It continues all his life.The functions may change and thus the stock of words or language fluctuates depending upon the functions it have.Thus a functional approach says that whatever function it expects to achieve is learnt ,there is also a conscious learning ,so there may be individual differences based on functions what one learns ,but the overall stock and therefore structure is simultaneously built based on these functions.\nThus we can say both subconscious ,automatic,natural,structural (chomsky''s way)along with its conscious,manual learning,nurture,functional(skinner,s way) of learning a language not only have the power to enrich individual language deficits but also expand the stock of words and language,thereby exposing the structure through evolution and the one who is exposed to both will be best learner.One may always weigh over others at times but ,they infact are simultaneous factors which affects one time or other.', '01 Feb ''14, 03:05', 0),
