('100168556', '100163135', 'users/100052000/luke-summerville', '1 = Deep Sleep\n2 = Coma\n3 = Playing Piano\n4 = Lucid Dreaming \n5 = Vegetative State \n1 = almost bottom left corner.\nBecause you are not awake and not aware.\n2 = bottom left corner.\nBecause you are really not awake and really not aware.\n3 = top right corner.\nBecause you are awake and you are aware.\n4 = top left corner.\nBecause you are not awake but you are aware. \n(Lucid Dreaming is when you''re aware that you''re dreaming.)\n5 = bottom right corner.\nBecause you are awake but not aware.\nHope this helps you out.', '10 Apr ''14, 13:29', 1),
