('100178973', '100158755', 'users/100104209/marcus', 'you mean to have sex?\nthere are a lot of ways to anwer this:\nthe sex you would like to have includes two people, you might have done something right if she is your girlfriend already.\nsex is a form of communication. To make it better, ask her about her fantasies. Also find out about her fantasies (Observe her behaviour) regarding likes and dislikes.\nevolutionary we are on this planet because our parents could reproduce. The finality of our system is to maintain the presence of our species. This doesn''t depend on how you think or act, but you are still responsible for your aims and for yourself. Don''t worry too much about how you''re going to have sex, have an aim in your life.\nSurely actual sex can also be pleasurable (when all the factors are right) but what do you do after the actual sex? wait? nothing? worry? You can''t have sex as much as you think about it. In fact sex motivates us in our minds, don''t waste it with worrying about having sex, or having sex. you don''t nee to short-circuit it all the time, use it as a motivation.', '06 May ''14, 06:26', 0),
